'''Bright''' was a nickname that was used among [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] [[Pilot/Legends|pilots]] who served with the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] and later the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]. It was used in reference to the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[TIE/Advanced starfighter (disambiguation)|TIE Advanced]] starfighter, as well as other "advanced" models of [[TIE series/Legends|TIE]] fighters.

